title: 419 Squad
body: <a href="http://www.jjc2uk.com/419bio.htm">Nigerian rappers</a>- yes they are really named after the 419ers.  I listened to a few of the MP3s on the site I was surprised - and strangely disappointed - that the songs weren't sung in all caps, and the lyrics didn't mention any dead relatives who had millions of dollars they need to transfer into a US account.
